DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, March 18th from 4–7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a tasting featuring the bold and expressive wines of Gamba Family Vineyards\, a Sonoma producer known for powerful old-vine Zinfandels and rich field blends that showcase the depth and character of the region.\nTasting Fee: $35 (Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded)\nFeatured Wines:\n• Gamba ‘Messana Vineyard’ Fountain Grove District Zinfandel – Deep and powerful with cherry compote\, vanilla\, sandalwood and vibrant red berry fruit layered with warm spice.\n• Gamba ‘Starr Road’ Zinfandel – Old-vine intensity showing raspberry preserves\, wild berries\, currant and black tea with supple tannins and a lingering finish.\n• Gamba Etrusca Velia Proprietary Red – A plush old-vine field blend bursting with dark berry fruit\, toasty oak and silky texture with notes of spice and polished tannins.\n• Gamba Family Ranches Zinfandel 2020 – Bold yet lively with raspberry\, blueberry\, leather and spice framed by bright acidity and balanced structure.\nDiscover the depth and richness of Gamba’s small-production Sonoma wines—buy a bottle and your tasting is free.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Gamba Family Vineyards Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR